quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  62,1,"Kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi hino seninnde Allah, LaamЙ—o, SeniiЙ—o, FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұo On"
  62,2,"Ko kanko nuli e humammbinneeЙ“e Й“en NulaaЙ—o jeyaaЙ—o e maЙ“Й“e, himo janngana Й“e Aayeeje Makko Й—en, o laЙ“Й“ina Й“e, o anndina Й“e Deftere nden e Sunna on, hay si tawiino ko adii Й—um, Й“e laatino e majjere Й“anngude"
  62,3,"(O nuli mo) kadi e woЙ—Й“e goo e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e hawrondiraali e Й“en taho. Ko Kanko woni FooluЙ—o, Г‘eeГұo On"
  62,4,"ЖҠum ko Й“ural Allah, Himo okka ngal mo O muuyani. Allah ko Jom Й“ural mawnngal"
  62,5,"Misal ronndinaaЙ“e Tawreeta Й“en refti Й“e golliraali nde, no wa'i wa mbabba ronndii mba defte. Misal yimЙ“e fennooЙ“e Aayeeje Alla Й—en bonii. Allah fewnataa yimЙ“e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  62,6,"Maaku: \"Ko onon yo HuudiЕӢkooЙ“e ! Si on aaЖҙike wonnde ko on yiЙ—aaЙ“e Allah ko wanaa yimЙ“e heddiiЙ“e Й“en, haray yelee maayde, si tawii ko on goonguЙ“e"
  62,7,"ЖҒe yelotaako nde muk, sabu ko juuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en ardini kon. Allah ko annduЙ—o tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  62,8,"Maaku: \"Ndee maayde nde dogoton, pellet, ko nde hawraynde e mon. Refti rutteЙ—on ka On annduЙ—o wirniiЙ—i e feeГұuЙ—i, O humpita on ko gollaynoЙ—on kon"
  62,9,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e ! Si juulde nden noddinanaama Гұalnde Juma, yaccee e jantagol Allah, acciton ngeyngu. Ko Й—um Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on, si tawno ko on annduЙ“e"
  62,10,"Si julde nden gasii, haray saakitee ka leydi, Й—aЙ“Й“on Й“ural Allah ngal [woni arsike], janntoron innde Allah ko Й—uuЙ—i, belajo'o on maloyte"
  62,11,"Si Й“e yi'ii ngeyngu maa fijindaaru, Й“e hammira ton, Й“e acce hiЙ—a darii. Maaku: \"Ko ko woni ka Allah kon Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude beleeЙ—e e njulaaku. Ko Allah Й“uri MoЖҙЖҙude e arsikooЙ“e Й“en"